Our contribution to A-Frame (https://aframe.io) for developers who need a HTML5 loader on their A-frame project.

There aren't many guides on how to create a reliable up to date loader, so we thought it'd be nice to share our solution with the wider community.

Feedback & improvements welcomed.
Team Voodoo (https://planetvoodoo.org)


Step 1:
Include the CSS somewhere in your document <head></head> section.

Step 2:
Add the JavaScript somewhere in your document <head></head> section.

Step 3:
Add the HTML to the top of your <body> section.
